{"tid":468703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"避狗炒車？ 自己友撞自己友2人傷","createTime":"2017-11-14T15:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T15:27:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9efb8b551ddab8d65805be51a9c650305768d1","tid":468703,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171114/20214275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F20214275&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a7f0b713\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F20214275&h=009a9d16\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171114/20214275</a><br />\n<br />\n避狗炒車？<br />\n自己友撞自己友2人傷<br />\n<br />\n5,636<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】葵涌道出九龍近瑪嘉烈醫院對開，昨天凌晨零時許，一批相識男女分乘兩部私家車，其間前行私家車報稱收慢閃避狗隻，隨後私家車煞掣不及，發生碰撞雙雙滑行至幾米外，撞向路邊花槽石壆始停下。<br />\n<br />\n意外中，一名18歲姓鄭女乘客及一名26歲姓蔡男乘客受輕傷，一併送院治理，警員到場調查意外原因。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n飛天黑膠袋惹禍　貨車撞貨車1人傷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n油麻地爆鹹水管　甘肅街封路改道"},{"pid":"63fdfd793e1fc392a77e3f97ac478fe75c283de7","tid":468703,"uid":142213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:25:29.000Z","msg":"又屈落啲狗到"},{"pid":"406343d774b4bfae85fd9ac6bfff4e9ad9a92d4d","tid":468703,"uid":71342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"兩件都係狗，總之就避狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}